# WE

A catchall repository of files used on WikiEducator,
especially JavaScript files used in the Widgets. It
is easier to edit them in the filesystem than in the
wiki's textareas.

## Vendored Libraries

The repository contains vendored libraries.

### jsgantt

A version of (jsGantt project)[https://code.google.com/p/jsgantt]
which was copyright 2009 Shlomy Gantz BlueBrick Inc. released
under the Modified BSD License.

### FlexSlider

Version 2.6.1 of (FlexSlider)[http://www.woothemes.com/flexslider/]
which was released under GPLv2.

### jQuery.popover

Version 1.1.2 of jQuery.popover is Copyright 2012 Davey
IJzermans, released under the MIT License.

